{"tid":1291752,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"十八區攪光復冇問題，但唔好除咗屌警察之外同五大訴求冇扣連","createTime":"2019-07-07T04:28:03.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-07T05:48:59.000Z","uid":30138,"like":10,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"e5c1671559fc51e7d093f82f125e96325898f003","tid":1291752,"uid":30138,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-07T04:28:03.000Z","msg":"好似打機咁，解支線冇問題。<br />\n<br />\n但你唔解主線係爆唔到機，你光復一次，個勢淡咗之後啲大陸人/大媽/廢老一樣會返嚟。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我哋要嘅係<span style=\"color: red;\">永久性既改變</span>，希望大家做唔同嘢嘅時候毋忘五大訴求，以致係因為政制同經濟唔民主先令到香港今日咁。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n香港人，加油！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"728e41fb7cf3cb70bb9e923b0f13a7d05b8dfbcb","tid":1291752,"uid":30138,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-07T04:29:53.000Z","msg":"pish"},{"pid":"65353099c6048788df5fd28fc404eabf520886c6","tid":1291752,"uid":30138,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-07T04:31:09.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"1806670b44444384153a18afdbad95a9f17d9e77","tid":1291752,"uid":30138,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-07T04:33:23.000Z","msg":"光復運動應該停止！唔好俾人帶風向！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1291272\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1291272</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n唔完全認同， 但睇法差唔多"},{"pid":"1b245f3b60125c6b6dcb2e122e095b5c46598564","tid":1291752,"uid":59815,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-07T04:34:04.000Z","msg":"同意<br />\n多區遊行係好事，接觸多d市民<br />\n但要集中五大訴求<br />\n光復真係一次兩次夠"},{"pid":"830e2464caadbd798b628a7f312be29ef398a70e","tid":1291752,"uid":30138,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-07T04:35:10.00